  "response": "Choosing the right guitar in the range of \u20b97,000 to \u20b98,000 depends on your preferences, playing style, and the type of guitar you're looking for (acoustic, electric, or classical). Here are some great options in this price range:\n\n### Acoustic Guitars:\n1. **Yamaha F310**  \n   - A popular choice for beginners and intermediate players.  \n   - Solid build quality and good sound for the price.  \n   - Price: Around \u20b97,500\u2013\u20b98,000.  \n\n2. **Fender FA-115**  \n   - A durable and stylish acoustic guitar.  \n   - Great for beginners with a comfortable neck and decent sound.  \n   - Price: Around \u20b97,500\u2013\u20b98,000.  \n\n3. **Kadence Legacy Series**  \n   - Affordable and reliable acoustic guitars with good tonal quality.  \n   - Ideal for beginners.  \n   - Price: Around \u20b97,000\u2013\u20b98,000.  \n\n4. **Bajaao Pathfinder**  \n   - A budget-friendly option with a decent build and sound.  \n   - Made in India, great value for money.  \n   - Price: Around \u20b97,000\u2013\u20b98,000.  \n\n### Classical Guitars:\n1. **Yamaha C40**  \n   - A well-known classical guitar with a warm tone.  \n   - Great for beginners learning fingerstyle or classical music.  \n   - Price: Around \u20b97,500\u2013\u20b98,000.  \n\n2. **Kadence Classical Acoustic Guitar**  \n   - Affordable and beginner-friendly.  \n   - Offers decent sound quality and playability.  \n   - Price: Around \u20b97,000\u2013\u20b98,000.  \n\n### Electric Guitars:\n1. **Fender Squier Bullet Strat**  \n   - A classic beginner electric guitar with a solid build.  \n   - Great for rock, blues, and other genres.  \n   - Price: Slightly above \u20b98,000, but worth considering.  \n\n2. **Yamaha Pacifica 012**  \n   - A versatile and well-built electric guitar.  \n   - Ideal for beginners exploring different styles.  \n   - Price: Slightly above \u20b98,000, but worth stretching your budget.  \n\n### Tips for Buying:\n1. **Play Before Buying**: If possible, try out the guitar to check its comfort, sound, and build quality.  \n2. **Check Accessories**: Some guitars come with a gig bag, strap, or picks, which can save you money.  \n3. **Buy from Reputable Sellers**: Purchase from trusted brands or sellers to avoid counterfeit products.  \n\nLet me know if you need more specific recommendations! \ud83c\udfb8",
